An update! Yes, again a long-overdue update with some rather small fixes in v1.6.0, however with the announcement that we're currently working hard behind the scenes to make v3 of stfc.pro a reality!

A summary of changes:

  • Re-vamped Alliance Lay-out The alliance details as well as the tournament alliance details had a different layout in comparison to the rest of the site. To keep things more universal, the layouts have been aligned.
  • STFC Shop! Yes, you read it right! We have a shop where you'll be able to get all kinds of apparel that's made by the community! Go get your mug, t-shirt or mousepad to show your support for the site!
  • lines!

I'd like to thank all contributors for supporting the site! I've created a special 'contributors' area on Discord, where I will discuss various new functions, give a chance for people to beta-test new functions as well as providing datasets (for example, event data). As a contributor, you can ask me for certain datasets!

","slug":"sept-updates-2025","version":"v1.6.0"},{"title":"June Updates!","date":"2025-09-23T00:00:00.000Z","html":"

Apologies for the long overdue update report! Many changes have been implemented over the past few months and lots of preparations have been made on the backend to ensure a smooth and stable website. Below is just a small grasp of changes that happened in the past months.

A summary of changes:

  • Re-vamped Alliance Lay-out The alliance details as well as the tournament alliance details had a different layout in comparison to the rest of the site. To keep things more universal, the layouts have been aligned.
  • New Alliance Metrics Two new Alliance metrics have been added: RSS Contribution and ISO contribution. Note that RSS contribution is linked to the current level of the alliance and gets reset after increasing the alliance level.
  • More CC icons! Even more CCs have applied through Discord and have been added! You can search for "cc:" to get a list of all known content creators.
  • STFC Shop! Yes, you read it right! We have a shop where you'll be able to get all kinds of apparel that's made by the community! Go get your mug, t-shirt or mousepad to show your support for the site!
  • Historical data Although not yet active on the website itself, historical data is now available for players and alliances! If you want to know your progress since 1-1-2025, it is now possible! We're working on getting data available on-site but you can always ask me in the #contributors channel in Discord.

I'd like to thank all contributors for supporting the site! I've created a special 'contributors' area on Discord, where I will discuss various new functions, give a chance for people to beta-test new functions as well as providing datasets (for example, event data). As a contributor, you can ask me for certain datasets!

","slug":"june-updates-2025","version":"1.5.0"}]}

{"count":3,"version":"v3.0.0","content":[{"title":"Welcome to v3!","date":"2025-12-31T00:00:00.000Z","html":"

New Account System

  • Login via Discord (more identity providers planned)
  • Profiles separated cleanly to reduce sync confusion
  • Clearer session state; fewer edge-case login issues
  • Foundations laid for an upcoming content-creator dashboard

Mobile Experience

  • Navigation rebuilt for small screens
  • Panels, drawers, and modals redesigned to avoid collisions
  • Reduced layout shift and improved load times on mobile networks

Player Pages

  • Dedicated stat pages for individual players
  • Cleaner URLs and faster lookups; no more modal-only views
  • Early groundwork for comparisons and historical tracking

Creator Partnerships

  • Collaboration with the STFC Officer Tool Discord
  • In-app visibility for their charts, crew builds, and reference guides
  • Shared effort to centralize resources instead of scattering them

Platform Rebuild

  • Full rewrite; underlying systems replaced instead of patched
  • Unified data layer between web, API, and future services
  • Stability, caching, and error-handling improved for upcoming features
","slug":"v3-initial-update","version":"v3.0.0"},{"title":"Septemberrr Updates!","date":"2025-09-23T00:00:00.000Z","html":"

An update! Yes, again a long-overdue update with some rather small fixes in v1.6.0, however with the announcement that we're currently working hard behind the scenes to make v3 of stfc.pro a reality!

A summary of changes:

  • Re-vamped Alliance Lay-out The alliance details as well as the tournament alliance details had a different layout in comparison to the rest of the site. To keep things more universal, the layouts have been aligned.
  • STFC Shop! Yes, you read it right! We have a shop where you'll be able to get all kinds of apparel that's made by the community! Go get your mug, t-shirt or mousepad to show your support for the site!
  • lines!

I'd like to thank all contributors for supporting the site! I've created a special 'contributors' area on Discord, where I will discuss various new functions, give a chance for people to beta-test new functions as well as providing datasets (for example, event data). As a contributor, you can ask me for certain datasets!

","slug":"sept-updates-2025","version":"v1.6.0"},{"title":"June Updates!","date":"2025-09-23T00:00:00.000Z","html":"

Apologies for the long overdue update report! Many changes have been implemented over the past few months and lots of preparations have been made on the backend to ensure a smooth and stable website. Below is just a small grasp of changes that happened in the past months.

A summary of changes:

  • Re-vamped Alliance Lay-out The alliance details as well as the tournament alliance details had a different layout in comparison to the rest of the site. To keep things more universal, the layouts have been aligned.
  • New Alliance Metrics Two new Alliance metrics have been added: RSS Contribution and ISO contribution. Note that RSS contribution is linked to the current level of the alliance and gets reset after increasing the alliance level.
  • More CC icons! Even more CCs have applied through Discord and have been added! You can search for "cc:" to get a list of all known content creators.
  • STFC Shop! Yes, you read it right! We have a shop where you'll be able to get all kinds of apparel that's made by the community! Go get your mug, t-shirt or mousepad to show your support for the site!
  • Historical data Although not yet active on the website itself, historical data is now available for players and alliances! If you want to know your progress since 1-1-2025, it is now possible! We're working on getting data available on-site but you can always ask me in the #contributors channel in Discord.

I'd like to thank all contributors for supporting the site! I've created a special 'contributors' area on Discord, where I will discuss various new functions, give a chance for people to beta-test new functions as well as providing datasets (for example, event data). As a contributor, you can ask me for certain datasets!
